collectionMetadata.name: Number of Palliative Home Care Visits
collectionMetadata.description:
Number of palliative home care visits. 

- From 2011 onwards, Home Palliative Care includes Nursing, Medical and Psychosocial.
- From 2015 onwards, Palliative Nursing, Palliative Medical and Psychosocial are streamlined into Home Palliative Care. Home Palliative Care visits consolidates the multiple services prior to 2015.
